    "body" : "<p>Assuming type TreeMap&lt;String,Integer&gt; :</p>\n\n<pre><code>for(Map.Entry&lt;String,Integer&gt; entry : treeMap.entrySet()) {\n  String key = entry.getKey();\n  Integer value = entry.getValue();\n\n  System.out.println(key + \" =&gt; \" + value);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>(key and Value types can be any class of course)</p>\n"
