    "body" : "<p>Using <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/google-collections/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Google Collections</a>, assuming K is your key type:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Maps.filterKeys(treeMap, new Predicate&lt;K&gt;() {\n  @Override\n  public boolean apply(K key) {\n    return false; //return true here if you need the entry to be in your new map\n  }});\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can use <code>filterEntries</code> instead if you need the value as well.</p>\n"
