    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just to point out the generic way to iterate over any map:</p>\n\n<pre><code> private &lt;K, V&gt; void iterateOverMap(Map&lt;K, V&gt; map) {\n    for (Map.Entry&lt;K, V&gt; entry : map.entrySet()) {\n        System.out.println(\"key -&gt;\" + entry.getKey() + \", value-&gt;\" + entry.getValue());\n    }\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
